    <h1>SECTION 1: Professional Photography & Visual Guide</h1>
    <h2>Hero Product Photos</h2>
    <p>Your photography determines Etsy success. Top sellers use consistent lighting, clean backgrounds, and lifestyle shots.</p>

    <h3>Lighting Setup</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>White seamless backdrop</li>
      <li>Two diffused LED or work lights</li>
      <li>White bounce reflector</li>
      <li>Tripod, no on-camera flash</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Key Photos to Capture</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>45° hero shot</li>
